The '''Kaminoan nano-virus vaccine''' was a vaccine made by [[Sayn Ta]] to protect [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] from the [[Kaminoan nano-virus]]. After Ta was killed by [[Kuma Nai]], the creator of the virus, the vaccine was injected into all clones.

